  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You've focused your combat training on rifle weapons. You gain the following benefits while wielding any of these weapons, if you are proficient with it:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You gain a +1 bonus to the weapon's damage rolls.</li>\n<li>When you score a critical hit with the weapon, you can roll one additional weapon damage die.</li>\n<li>When you take the Attack action, you can choose to forgo one or more attacks to  <strong>scramble</strong>. For each attack you forgo, you can move up to 10 feet without provoking opportunity attacks.</li></ul>",
